WEBVTT

00:00.953 --> 00:02.772
Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.773 --> 00:05.772
I don't even know what's
real anymore, and what is...

00:05.773 --> 00:08.362
We'll just figure it out,
because you're real to me.

00:08.363 --> 00:11.562
You know, if there's anything I can do

00:11.563 --> 00:13.732
to help...

00:13.733 --> 00:16.582
- Cal came and got me.
- You're here.

00:16.583 --> 00:19.552
He said this is where I'm supposed to be.

00:19.553 --> 00:20.622
They are trying to kill me,

00:20.623 --> 00:21.722
and they will kill you.

00:23.573 --> 00:25.552
Come on, Alison. Come back with me.

00:26.633 --> 00:28.692
Go!

00:28.693 --> 00:31.522
- I want you to take the walk.
- Steve's walk?

00:31.523 --> 00:33.742
If you don't do the walk, I
will tell Sarah everything.

00:33.743 --> 00:35.682
I'll tell her you don't believe.

00:35.683 --> 00:39.572
When did you know about...
you always hear the elders

00:39.573 --> 00:41.722
talking about the moment
when they felt it, The Light.

00:41.723 --> 00:45.582
Closest thing to it, when I met your mom.

00:45.583 --> 00:47.652
- Stop.
- You know, she can just...

00:47.653 --> 00:49.572
What's going on?

00:49.573 --> 00:51.622
- Lift all my doubts.
- And he's lying to you.

